{"tid":2082951,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"喜歡人不犯法 可我也只能到喜歡為止了","createTime":"2020-06-28T12:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T03:46:14.000Z","uid":283870,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"24ee729c9b303c605ed035e6d1f5c8c7252448c4","tid":2082951,"uid":283870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:16:54.000Z","msg":"「想想說人生無悔，都是賭氣的話。人生若無悔，那該多無趣啊。葉先生，說句真心話，我心裡有過你。我把這話告訴你也沒什麼。喜歡人不犯法，可我也只能到喜歡為止了。這些話我沒對誰說過，今晚見了你，不知道為什麼就都說出來了。就讓你我的恩怨像盤棋一樣，保留在那兒。你多保重。」<br />\n<br />\n話雖如此，但<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/06cmusA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06cmusA.png&h=dc9cdcf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你只要回一句，我就心滿意足了。"},{"pid":"8ed4269fe72afee674253a8a02b789b23264755a","tid":2082951,"uid":283870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n哭𠹌咗"},{"pid":"da5f5f3fa75c5ca61da5fe1baebc7e8c9172e28c","tid":2082951,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"但現實往往殘酷的是<br />\n她根本心裏從來沒有過你"},{"pid":"ec72c5b89d366979695a76861f4c916fabdf97aa","tid":2082951,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T20:10:40.000Z","msg":"我唔做偵探都真係嘥咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fff21e537f3854bf00c93de812e141d55358a65","tid":2082951,"uid":283870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec72c5b89d366979695a76861f4c916fabdf97aa","tid":2082951,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T20:10:40.000Z","msg":"我唔做偵探都真係嘥咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T03:46:14.000Z","msg":"IP都唔使check？"}]}